Briozoarios de tres esteros adyacentes a Mazatlán, Costa Noroeste de MéxicoFirst report of the bryozoan species, Amathia distans, A. semiconvotuta, Anguinella palmata, Bugula neritina, Membranipora tuberculata, Thalamoporelta gothica y Zoobotryon verticillatum from estuars near to Mazatlán (Sinaloa), Mexico. Brief comments on ecological parameters and associated fauna are given.